channel.title: Souliced - Need Server developer. ASAP

Hi, I'm the owner of a server called Soul iced, I'm looking for someone who can actually help code and develop the server along side with me as my old developer doesn't have time to anymore. If anyone is interested, the server is a 718 Citellum source. I've done a few tweaks myself but I'll need someone help with the cache work, shops, combat and other tweaks.
My skype is : Jackhampson
if you're interested please feel free to add me.
